org.jamesframework.ext.problems.objectives.evaluations

Class WeightedIndexEvaluation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jamesframework.ext.problems.objectives.evaluations.WeightedIndexEvaluation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Evaluation

    public class WeightedIndexEvaluation
extends Object
implements Evaluation
    Evaluation produced by a weighted index. Contains evaluations produced by the underlying objectives and the respective weights. The double value is computed as a weighted sum of the contained objectives' double values where the sign of minimizing objectives is flipped because a weighted index is always maximized.
    Author:
    Herman De Beukelaer
